It's still on my list to reforge BSgenome.Mmusculus.UCSC.mm10.masked. I 
reforged BSgenome.Mmusculus.UCSC.mm10 back in June after the UCSC folks 
updated the mm10 genome and tracks (see 
https://github.com/Bioconductor/GenomeInfoDb/issues/27). But 
BSgenome.Mmusculus.UCSC.mm10.masked is still based on the old 
BSgenome.Mmusculus.UCSC.mm10 and needs to be resynced with the new one.

I'll do this today. Sorry for the inconvenience.

H.

